headline: TDY Q3 Deep Dive: Mixed Market Trends and Resilient Defense Demand Shape Outlook
summary: Digital imaging and instrumentation provider Teledyne (NYSE:TDY) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 6.7% year on year to $1.54 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $5.57 per share was 1.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
